{
  "text": "Yesterday you stated \"the harvest is now. There is not at this time any reason to include efforts upon these distortions toward longevity, but rather to encourage distortions towards the heart of self. For this which resides clearly in the violet-ray energy field will determine the harvest of each mind/body/spirit complex. \" Could you tell us how to seek or the best way to seek the heart of self? I am Ra. We have given you this information in several wordings. However, we can only say the material for your understanding is the self: the mind/body/spirit complex. You have been given information upon healing, as you call this distortion. This information may be seen in a more general context as ways to understand the self. The understanding, experiencing, accepting, and merging of self with self and with other-self, and finally with the Creator, is the path to the heart of self. In each infinitesimal part of your self resides the One in all of Its power. Therefore, we can only encourage these lines of contemplation, always stating the prerequisite of meditation, contemplation, or prayer as a means of subjectively/objectively using or combining various understandings to enhance the seeking process. Without such a method of reversing the analytical process, one could not integrate into unity the many understandings gained in such seeking.",
  "timestamps": {
    "segment": [
      {
        "segment": "Yesterday you stated \"the harvest is now.",
        "start_offset": 0,
        "end_offset": 41,
        "start": 1.38,
        "end": 5.8
      },
      {
        "segment": "There is not at this time any reason to include efforts upon these distortions toward longevity, but rather to encourage distortions towards the heart of self.",
        "start_offset": 42,
        "end_offset": 201,
        "start": 5.9,
        "end": 31.161
      },
      {
        "segment": "For this which resides clearly in the violet-ray energy field will determine the harvest of each mind/body/spirit complex.",
        "start_offset": 202,
        "end_offset": 324,
        "start": 31.181,
        "end": 40.181
      },
      {
        "segment": "Could you tell us how to seek or the best way to seek the heart of self?",
        "start_offset": 327,
        "end_offset": 399,
        "start": 40.201,
        "end": 43.422
      },
      {
        "segment": "I am Ra.",
        "start_offset": 400,
        "end_offset": 408,
        "start": 43.442,
        "end": 43.762
      },
      {
        "segment": "We have given you this information in several wordings.",
        "start_offset": 409,
        "end_offset": 464,
        "start": 43.782,
        "end": 53.862
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, we can only say the material for your understanding is the self: the mind/body/spirit complex.",
        "start_offset": 465,
        "end_offset": 568,
        "start": 54.862,
        "end": 78.863
      },
      {
        "segment": "You have been given information upon healing, as you call this distortion.",
        "start_offset": 569,
        "end_offset": 643,
        "start": 80.323,
        "end": 93.683
      },
      {
        "segment": "This information may be seen in a more general context as ways to understand the self.",
        "start_offset": 644,
        "end_offset": 730,
        "start": 95.503,
        "end": 114.804
      },
      {
        "segment": "The understanding, experiencing, accepting, and merging of self with self and with other-self, and finally with the Creator, is the path to the heart of self.",
        "start_offset": 731,
        "end_offset": 889,
        "start": 116.524,
        "end": 145.865
      },
      {
        "segment": "In each infinitesimal part of your self resides the One in all of Its power.",
        "start_offset": 890,
        "end_offset": 966,
        "start": 147.105,
        "end": 165.346
      },
      {
        "segment": "Therefore, we can only encourage these lines of contemplation, always stating the prerequisite of meditation, contemplation, or prayer as a means of subjectively/objectively using or combining various understandings to enhance the seeking process.",
        "start_offset": 967,
        "end_offset": 1214,
        "start": 167.106,
        "end": 222.848
      },
      {
        "segment": "Without such a method of reversing the analytical process, one could not integrate into unity the many understandings gained in such seeking.",
        "start_offset": 1215,
        "end_offset": 1356,
        "start": 223.888,
        "end": 257.649
      }
    ],
